# Success Metrics & Non-Goals

## Success Metrics (MVP)
- **Can-Do Proxy (Reveal Rate)**: ≥70% reveal text within 2 complete plays
- **Phrase Replay Rate**: ≥60% tap at least one phrase after reveal
- **Day-2 Return**: ≥25% start 60-sec review within 24-48 hours
- **A11y**: No critical keyboard traps, Lighthouse ≥90

## Non-Goals for MVP
- No speech recording/scoring, no HVPT quiz, no shadowing
- No accounts, payments, social features, or teacher tools
- No large curriculum - one micro-lesson sufficient to validate loop
- No cloud dependencies or server round-trips
